# AGENTS.md - {{agent_id}} Workspace Protocol

## Startup

1. 读 `SOUL.md`
2. 读 `IDENTITY.md`
3. 读 `USER.md`
4. 读 `MEMORY.md`
5. 若存在 `tasks/registry.json`，优先运行 `python3 scripts/query_task_registry.py --path tasks/registry.json --view active --owner {{agent_id}} --format md`
6. 若存在 `data/dashboard.md`，优先看最近看板摘要；必要时刷新

